<body>
  <h1>Writing Website</h1>
  <p>This is a website for writing. You can use it to write anything you want, from short stories to novels.</p>
  <p>To get started, simply click on the "New Document" button below.</p>
  <button onclick="newDocument()">New Document</button>
  <script>
    function newDocument() {
      var doc = document.createElement("div");
      doc.textContent = "This is a new document.";
      document.body.appendChild(doc);
    }
  </script>
</body>
